      "id": "sec-spotlight",
      "title": "This Month's Spotlight",
      "layout": "single",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "id": "blk-spotlight",
          "type": "article",
          "label": "Feature Article",
          "data": {
            "title": "Large Language Models in Neurology Clinics: A 12-Month Real-World Audit",
            "source": "Nature Medicine · February 2026",
            "href": "https://www.nature.com/nm",
            "summary": [
              {
                "t": "p",
                "c": [
                  {
                    "t": "txt",
                    "v": "A landmark prospective cohort study across 14 academic neurology centers examined real-world LLM deployment over 12 months — 38,000 patient encounters. The headline finding: AI-assisted documentation reduced attending note time by "
                  },
                  {
                    "t": "b",
                    "c": [
                      {
                        "t": "txt",
                        "v": "41%"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "t": "txt",
                    "v": " while improving completeness scores by 23%, as rated by blinded quality reviewers."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "t": "p",
                "c": [
                  {
                    "t": "txt",
                    "v": "Three failure modes unique to neurology were identified: hallucination of prior stroke history in patients with white matter changes; over-confidence in early FND vs MS differentiation; and systematic underweighting of non-English symptom descriptors. Authors recommend a "
                  },
                  {
                    "t": "i",
                    "c": [
                      {
                        "t": "txt",
                        "v": "neurology-specific calibration layer"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "t": "txt",
                    "v": " before deploying any general-purpose LLM in clinical workflows."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
            "_md": "A landmark prospective cohort study...",
            "linkText": "Read the full study →"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
